summary: This mod adds a new house (with safe containers) and a new tomb (also with safe container) for the Dragonborn.
descriptionHtml:
This is my fisrt mod.

This mod basically adds a small shack and tomb near the abandoned prison. The location has it\\\\\\\'s own map marker so I trust you will find it easily.

The tomb is the Dragonborn\\\\\\\'s own tomb. It contains a throne room, and some other valuable loot.
The use is usable as a player home, it contains basic containers, a bed and some ingredients

If you have any suggestions or bug reports, please let me know.
author: MasterGamer1101
